snippet: CALIFORNIA MARKET, Sept. 6.--There is no Flour arriving worthy of notice, and very little expected. City stocks are heavy. With the tight receipts, the stock of some articles will be reduced very low....
lead_paragraph: CALIFORNIA MARKET, Sept. 6.--There is no Flour arriving worthy of notice, and very little expected. City stocks are heavy. With the tight receipts, the stock of some articles will be reduced very low.
